{"tid":1032894,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【毒遊】六日五夜鹿兒島之旅","createTime":"2019-02-22T17:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T16:18:55.000Z","uid":105624,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ade8bf948a41b7f719908a93b79313a388097ae8","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"首先係到多謝咁多位喺我個求助post留過言同比過意見我嘅巴/絲打(如果有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n話說因為呢個月爆咗AL要清曬佢，咁啱由遇到hk express做sale(雖然都唔係好平嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。<br />\n其實本身都無目的地，係純粹亂撳，邊到平就去邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁撳撳下發覺鹿兒島機票最平而又未去過喎(本身仲要以為鹿兒島係有好多鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，同埋啲時間又幾啱我(可以走最少嘅堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，咁一時即興衝昏頭腦就買咗機票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而因為我太即興就話要去旅行，身邊啲fd子都請唔到假/無假陪我去(<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(其實係毒撚無乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span>，所以係咁多個巧合下，我就開始咗呢個毒遊6日5夜嘅鹿兒島啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f1d24914b3dc99df4dbc34c0922b94e5806ba3","tid":1032894,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T17:09:10.000Z","msg":"試下去熊本個火山"},{"pid":"bb9835678e77bf0bf13f4313cbc07cc652f1deaa","tid":1032894,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:28:12.000Z","msg":"想問一家大細去係咪會好悶，多小朋友"},{"pid":"95169eeaa4b42f08a548ddb090500f64f4e4ecf6","tid":1032894,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:05:14.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02c7b96d37845a05302763507063677ef88f453","tid":1032894,"uid":63177,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bb9835678e77bf0bf13f4313cbc07cc652f1deaa","tid":1032894,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:28:12.000Z","msg":"想問一家大細去係咪會好悶，多小朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"鹿兒島無大型主題樂園<br />\n但有簡單水族館 山山水水 公園<br />\n日本永遠都唔會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d755dce6a55791d858794311068f1d6fadca9521","tid":1032894,"uid":162713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T02:21:28.000Z","msg":"鹿兒島正阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f2d968c817cb5e1f8e5a70c942a786e310493c","tid":1032894,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b30ee863e1d5f27cc2ea981ef7e968d6a86b6f","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb9835678e77bf0bf13f4313cbc07cc652f1deaa","tid":1032894,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:28:12.000Z","msg":"想問一家大細去係咪會好悶，多小朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"唔會呀，我個人覺得比東京，大阪京都嗰啲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過你講大型主題公園南九州好似無，但係都好多嘢啱親子活動呀，騎下馬，去牧場睇牛牛，浸下溫泉嗰啲都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 一嚟我覺得啲風景靚啲，二嚟少啲遊客，最緊要係無大阪東京嗰啲熱門旅遊區咁多蝗！，希望將來，以後大陸都唔會有飛南九州嘅航線，唔係又淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一缺點真係啲交通無咁方便囉，我覺得你兩個人搭巴士還好，湊小朋友去一定要自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b967b2cff13de01b8e5c60a2dee81cb52b2c62f","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2f2d968c817cb5e1f8e5a70c942a786e310493c","tid":1032894,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"放心，唔會走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f64eb2c8877a60b774524bb4e4a7653cfe1d13","tid":1032894,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b967b2cff13de01b8e5c60a2dee81cb52b2c62f","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2f2d968c817cb5e1f8e5a70c942a786e310493c","tid":1032894,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"放心，唔會走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cee8783059301fe7ffdd7fad44cd75af31200bc","tid":1032894,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b967b2cff13de01b8e5c60a2dee81cb52b2c62f","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2f2d968c817cb5e1f8e5a70c942a786e310493c","tid":1032894,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\