":{"pid":"9b967b2cff13de01b8e5c60a2dee81cb52b2c62f","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"放心，唔會走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:16:24.000Z","msg":"放心喎，我記得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排真係好忙，呢個禮拜會逐漸出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">因為呢個post，身邊好多人起咗我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我出埋個遊記就唔會再用呢個acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbf9c1425edc8166352eec79ea33f0d7fffab0a","tid":1032894,"uid":75525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"快啦, 起碼比個行程簡介睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c062dbd3fa9d12f6e61e3e36450d35d04359d259","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:56:43.000Z","msg":"原來拖下拖下都差唔多成個月，同咁多位巴打講聲唔好意思先，因為轉咗新工都比較忙，係最近先得閒翻少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (加上自己不嬲好hea底，嚴重拖延症<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n依家日日都翻去做狗咁，好掛住自己一個係鹿兒島自由自在嘅時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話講完，講翻我個行程先 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>Day 1</strong><br />\n四點幾已經起身，可能因為未試過搭咁早飛機去，又或者第一次自己一個去旅行，一直有種勁不安嘅感覺，又好驚塞車/miss咗班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩最後都順利上到飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u9f71MV_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu9f71MV_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=07594561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概當地時間十一點三左右到鹿兒島機場，聽到機身滴滴達達聲，仆街原來落雨。即刻灰咗，灰埋右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然都未plan好去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/joBRZzl_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjoBRZzl_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=8c2f774a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出到機場竟然有個足湯都幾吸引，但無時間亦都無心情浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8zvbcX5_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8zvbcX5_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity&h=37716cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯有去咗中央站先，換埋張jr pass同埋睇下劃唔劃到特色列車啲位先再算<br />\n<br />\n啲機場巴士唔難搵，一出到機場門口就會見到去不同目的地嘅巴士。我去中央站，所以搭紅色線2號巴士 (記得要買咗飛先上車呀，同埋留意翻啲班次，有某啲班次會快啲，有啲又會慢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3Vi5qOr_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3Vi5qOr_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=54cfc22b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概9個字到就由鹿兒島機場去到中央站啦(其實我住天文館，但因為要換jr pass嗰啲所以先係到落。建議大家揀翻中央站附近嘅酒店，因為真係方便好多，又唔洗比多程電車錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yzJQSO3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyzJQSO3.jpg&h=65bb4159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身draft咗想搭嘅特色列車都無曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後搞咗一輪，要個姐姐幫我查嚟查去(真係好多謝個姐姐無嫌我煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 終於換到兩種想搭嘅觀光列車(係好熱門嘅指宿玉手箱號同埋海幸山幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 行程去到呢刻亦終於叫做定好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DAaxpDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDAaxpDK.jpg&h=54df45b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劃曬位買埋飛，仲依然係落緊大雨，原定行程迫住要取消曬，唯有翻咗酒店放低啲行李再作打算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路行見到好多電車，初初到埗覺得好新奇係咁影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後發覺其實都無乜特別，啫係等於港島嘅叮叮，仲要貴好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (劃一170yen) 雖則喺鹿兒島市內搭佢地真係好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ofej9qF_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOfej9qF_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=076cb4bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去緊酒店嘅途中有個位有好多夜總會，唔知有無巴打試過呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (後尾發現天文館嗰面有幾條街去到夜晚都好精彩，有興趣嘅巴打可以試下再包膠一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sXRfA3p_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsXRfA3p_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=24597dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻到酒店擺好嘅嘢都已經成2點半，開始好肚餓，搵咗陣決定去某位巴打介紹嘅炸豬排飯啦<br />\n<br />\n依然keep住落雨，而且個人覺得個位置都有少少偏，行咗差唔多4個字終於去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能因為落雨/ 就快夠鐘落場 所以無乜人食，唔洗排隊都食到實在太好<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlFsPKD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwlFsPKD.jpg&h=717664cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係講笑，真係好撚好味呀！我嗰下差少少好似食神入面個薛家燕咁嗌出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (我諗可能加上我真係太攰太肚餓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n個人覺得真係必食，1000yen激高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gIyJTnT_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgIyJTnT_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=04423117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完飯都差唔多4點，雖然都仲落住雨，但我又唔甘心咁就浪費咗一日，上網search下究竟有啲咩地方去啦，搵搵下見到某網站話城山展望台可以睇到好靚嘅櫻島火山，既然今日偷唔到時間去櫻島，就上去遠距離望下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路嘅風景<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3xQjnyR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3xQjnyR.jpg&h=3ccf4c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LjlfIga_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLjlfIga_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=d4d68894&s={SIZE}\" />]<br />\n<br />\n行咗半個鐘到終於到，嚟到先發現原來個城山展望台係需要行山上去嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o40FUbv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fo40FUbv.jpg&h=eacdca7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再行多五分鐘，終於到咗入口，開始有啲淆底，因為已經4點幾，仲係落緊雨，又唔知幾時天黑，而且除咗我附近一條友都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰時係抱住&quot;一場嚟到，唔係唔上埋去睇呀，反正唔去都無嘢做架啦&rdquo;嘅心態上去，宜加諗翻起都覺得自己cls，嗰時點解可以咁大膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IwldpwR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIwldpwR.jpg&h=0ab286e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路上去都係得自己一個(邊有人好似我咁白痴落雨走嚟行山呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，有啲位又好暗好黑，加上個天開始黑，真心幾淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過諗到一陣可以睇到美麗嘅櫻島火山，一切都係值得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行咗三個字到，終於到啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A0GvdsP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FA0GvdsP.jpg&h=57a07a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上到去搵咗幾分鐘，心諗搵極都搵唔到個火山嘅? 係去錯地方，定係仲要再上呢 (但係已經無路行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n又搵咗陣，又見到有個好大嘅牌介紹櫻島火山，再上網搵翻人地影嘅相，對翻個位置先發<br />\n發覺原來係啲雲定唔知霧遮住曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係頹到pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PmZ4g7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPmZ4g7e.jpg&h=5b4c080b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲風景都幾靚嘅(唯有咁樣安慰自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/G5rBtgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FG5rBtgr.jpg&h=cba50ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留咗十分鐘到，行(跑，因為個天開始黑得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)翻落山。鳩fing fing行咗去個市政廳嘅物體<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i3Q0gVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi3Q0gVB.jpg&h=d440a11a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入去休息咗陣，就再周圍fing下<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/C6cLbD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FC6cLbD9.jpg&h=4f33f490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後fing到8點幾就翻翻去中央站食嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RpmXaq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRpmXaq1.jpg&h=028c2680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDAY1 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知仲有無人睇呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b24b5a11b21ecc7128c69de4d5b6bb17b3e133","tid":1032894,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T19:00:02.000Z","msg":"找數真漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f53d1defbe15586ed9efc838a1e92089fbb486","tid":1032894,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T23:14:20.000Z","msg":"鹿兒島有冇得shopping?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea52b9d504b0fa927b7164ebaa04c03f608bc1f8","tid":1032894,"uid":121562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"你冇買pass？<br />\n任搭觀光巴士，電車同去櫻島既船<br />\n唔使行上山架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d696c35560a3835a6610d47ff134ead10b9a5a8","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77b24b5a11b21ecc7128c69de4d5b6bb17b3e133","tid":1032894,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T19:00:02.000Z","msg":"找數真漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:00:15.000Z","msg":"洗乜講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過巴打咁夜都唔瞓嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3444bb0081cc10a42edf077f939d8b2ca5747cf7","tid":1032894,"uid":83340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:18:30.000Z","msg":"6日係哂鹿兒島？<br />\n有無去櫻島，枕椅？"},{"pid":"49a3ffd93a5bb5b65b7eb757ad8dd392182391d2","tid":1032894,"uid":105624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40f53d1defbe15586ed9efc838a1e92089fbb486","tid":1032894,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":